articles.title: William and Kate will fly to Singapore for the final of the Prince of Wales's Earthshot Prize - Daily Mail
articles.description: William and Kate (pictured) will travel to the south east Asian country in November after it was selected as the destination of the third annual awards ceremony for the Prince's Earthshot prize.
articles.content:
The Prince and Princess of Wales will travel to Singapore later this year for the final of William's environmental award.
